=== Mini-finding: what a Page<T> (not Slice<T>) would have cost, every request ===
SELECT count(*) FROM transaction;  -- the query Spring Data fires once per
                                    -- Page<T> request in addition to the content query
--- cold ---
 Finalize Aggregate  (cost=71870.88..71870.89 rows=1 width=8) (actual time=1396.906..1406.106 rows=1 loops=1)
   Buffers: shared hit=14301 read=30528
   ->  Gather  (cost=71870.67..71870.88 rows=2 width=8) (actual time=1396.708..1406.092 rows=3 loops=1)
         Workers Planned: 2
         Workers Launched: 2
         Buffers: shared hit=14301 read=30528
         ->  Partial Aggregate  (cost=70870.67..70870.68 rows=1 width=8) (actual time=1384.425..1384.426 rows=1 loops=3)
               Buffers: shared hit=14301 read=30528
               ->  Parallel Seq Scan on transaction  (cost=0.00..65662.33 rows=2083333 width=0) (actual time=0.076..1245.881 rows=1666667 loops=3)
                     Buffers: shared hit=14301 read=30528
 Planning:
   Buffers: shared hit=85
 Planning Time: 0.678 ms
 Execution Time: 1406.325 ms

--- warm ---
 Finalize Aggregate  (cost=71870.88..71870.89 rows=1 width=8) (actual time=388.647..395.983 rows=1 loops=1)
   Buffers: shared hit=14314 read=30515
   ->  Gather  (cost=71870.67..71870.88 rows=2 width=8) (actual time=388.426..395.968 rows=3 loops=1)
         Workers Planned: 2
         Workers Launched: 2
         Buffers: shared hit=14314 read=30515
         ->  Partial Aggregate  (cost=70870.67..70870.68 rows=1 width=8) (actual time=380.446..380.448 rows=1 loops=3)
               Buffers: shared hit=14314 read=30515
               ->  Parallel Seq Scan on transaction  (cost=0.00..65662.33 rows=2083333 width=0) (actual time=0.031..244.781 rows=1666667 loops=3)
                     Buffers: shared hit=14314 read=30515
 Planning:
   Buffers: shared hit=85
 Planning Time: 0.687 ms
 Execution Time: 396.292 ms
-- Note: MVCC visibility means Postgres can't answer count(*) from the index
-- alone; it's a full (parallel) seq scan every time, independent of depth or
-- page size. Fixed tax that would land on EVERY Page<T> request, on top of
-- whichever content query (OFFSET or keyset) ran alongside it.

